OL,3,CPassengers boarding trains without a
OL,4,Cticket will face fines on more routes
OL,6,FPassengers who board trains without a
OL,7,Fticket face being fined on more lines
OL,8,Ffrom next month.
OL,10,FTransport for Wales (TfW) says it is
OL,11,Fexpanding its penalty fare zones from
OL,12,FMonday, 9 September.
OL,14,FIt means passengers boarding certain
OL,15,Flines without a ticket, or without
OL,16,Ftapping pay as you go where it is
OL,17,Favailable, will face a fine of double
OL,18,Fthe ticket fare, or #20, depending on
OL,19,Fwhich is greater.
