OL,6,FThe expanded zone will affect the
OL,7,Fmajority of trains in south Wales,
OL,8,Fincluding the Aberdare, Barry,
OL,9,FBridgend, Coryton, Ebbw Vale, Merthyr,
OL,10,FPenarth, Rhymney, and Treherbert lines.
OL,12,FCurrently, the penalty fare zone lines
OL,13,Fimpact journeys between the Severn
OL,14,FTunnel Junction and Carmarthen, and
OL,15,Fthe Shrewsbury to Birmingham line.
