OL,6,FWhen the expanded zone kicks in,
OL,7,Fpassengers are being advised they will
OL,8,Fnot be able to buy a ticket on the
OL,9,Ftrain, and instead should either buy a
OL,10,Fticket online, at the station or use
OL,11,Fthe pay as you go system.
OL,13,FServices in north Wales will be mostly
OL,14,Funaffected, however, the expansion
OL,15,Fwill apply to the Welsh Marches line,
OL,16,Fwhich runs from south Wales to
OL,17,FManchester.
