OL,3,CPassengers boarding trains without a
OL,4,Cticket will face fines on more routes
OL,6,FIn a statement, TfW said: "From 9
OL,7,FSeptember the penalty fare zone will
OL,8,Fbe extended across the South Wales
OL,9,FMetro area including Treherbert,
OL,10,FAderdare and Merthyr Lines plus
OL,11,FRhymney, Ebbw Vale, Barry and Vale of
OL,12,FGlamorgan Line.
OL,14,F"The expansion also covers the Marches
OL,15,Fline which runs from South Wales to
OL,16,FManchester. This builds on the
OL,17,Fexisting penalty fares schemes which
OL,18,Falready exist on the Shrewsbury to
OL,19,FBirmingham line and the South Wales
OL,20,FMainline.
